'''Matthew Berry''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed [[Brock Lar]], [[Gryphon]], and ''[[Martika]]'' along with [[Craig Farr]], in the "[[Design An Alien]]" contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the 16 years and older category. He was 18 at the time his entry was published.

